	<string id="agroprom_get_military_documents_task_name">
	<text>Find the military documents</text>
</string>
<string id="agroprom_get_military_documents_task_text">
	<text>Sidorovich and other traders are interested in documents containing information about the Center of the Zone. The documents are located in the former Agroprom Research Institute building and are guarded by the military.</text>
</string>

<string id="agr_meet_krot_band_task_name">
	<text>Meet with Mole</text>
</string>
<string id="agr_meet_krot_band_task_text">
	<text>Grey said that the diggers from Mole's group found the Gunslinger’s stash in the Agroprom area. I need to meet with Mole and get more details.</text>
</string>

<string id="agroprom_find_gunslinger_cache_name">
	<text>Gunslinger group's stash</text>
</string>
<string id="agroprom_find_gunslinger_cache_text">
	<text>It turns out the diggers couldn't find the Gunslinger’s stash. Mole is certain that the stash is located in the underground part of Agroprom, on the lowest level.</text>
</string>

<string id="agr_help_stalkers_name">
	<text>Help the stalkers</text>
</string>
<string id="agr_help_stalkers_text">
	<text>A military unit attacked the diggers from Mole's group at the factory. I need to help the stalkers.</text>
</string>

<string id="agr_help_krot_name">
	<text>Rescue Mole</text>
</string>
<string id="agr_help_krot_text">
	<text>The leader of the local diggers, Mole, was cornered by the military in the central courtyard of the factory. I need to help him.</text>
</string>

<string id="agr_find_ghost_name">
	<text>Find out what happened to Ghost</text>
</string>
<string id="agr_find_ghost_text">
	<text>There was a message from someone named Ghost in the Gunslinger group’s stash. Most likely, Ghost is also a member of the group. I need to find him.</text>
</string>


